==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Avenger
<hw>A*ven"ger</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One
who avenges or vindicates; <as>as, an <ex>avenger</ex> of
blood</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One who takes vengeance.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Milton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Avengeress</ent>⟦br⟧
